ight-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25</span></span></a> - Simple task runner with a terse syntax.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mysticatea/npm-run-all\">npm-run-all</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mysticatea/npm-run-all\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5k</span></span></a> - Fully featured task runner.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/coderaiser/redrun\">redrun</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/coderaiser/redrun\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">109</span></span></a> - Expand scripts from package.json to improve execution speed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"file-watchers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#file-watchers\" aria-label=\"file watchers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>File Watchers</h2>\n<p>Tools to watch your source files and run a build command whenever any of the files change.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Qard/onchange\">onchange</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Qard/onchange\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">776</span></span></a> - <code class=\"language-text\">onchange &lt;glob&gt; -- &lt;command&gt;</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mikeal/watch\">watch</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mikeal/watch\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a> - <code class=\"language-text\">watch &lt;command&gt; &lt;directory&gt;</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"dev-servers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dev-servers\" aria-label=\"dev servers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Dev Servers</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/indexzero/http-server\">http-server</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/indexzero/http-server\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12.2k</span></span></a> - Simple zero-configuration command-line http server.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tapio/live-server\">live-server</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tapio/live-server\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4k</span></span></a> - Simple development http server with live reload capability.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cross-platform-utilities\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cross-platform-utilities\" aria-label=\"cross platform utilities permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cross-platform Utilities</h2>\n<p>Utilities to perform common command-line tasks without worrying about cross-platform compatibility.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/isaacs/rimraf\">rimraf</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/isaacs/rimraf\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.9k</span></span></a> - Delete files or directories; like <code class=\"language-text\">rm -rf</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/del-cli\">del-cli</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/del-cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">264</span></span></a> - Safer file and folder deletion.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/substack/node-mkdirp\">mkdirp</a> - Create a directory, creating parent directories if needed; like <code class=\"language-text\">mkdir -p</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/davglass/cpr\">cpr</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/davglass/cpr\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">76</span></span></a> - <code class=\"language-text\">cp -r</code> for Node.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/cpy-cli\">cpy-cli</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/cpy-cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">278</span></span></a> - File/directory copying/renaming.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/calvinmetcalf/copyfiles\">copyfiles</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/calvinmetcalf/copyfiles\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left